    {
      "id": "PopularPost88507",
      "post_content": "You know, the funny thing about the human skeleton is that many of the smaller bones are attached to each other only by ligaments and muscle. In other words, once those things rot there is nothing holding your kneecaps to your legs. In fact, without all the ligaments in your spinal column, the vertebrae are just kind of stacked on top of each other.  \n  \nSo, long story short, if ever a necromancer were to start raising skeletons we'd have nothing to worry about as they would not be able to get up and start walking.",
      "posted_by": "allmighty_abacus",
      "html": "<div class=\"post oddItem\" id=\"PopularPost88507\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl03_post\">You know, the funny thing about the human skeleton is that many of the smaller bones are attached to each other only by ligaments and muscle. In other words, once those things rot there is nothing holding your kneecaps to your legs. In fact, without all the ligaments in your spinal column, the vertebrae are just kind of stacked on top of each other.<br/><br/>So, long story short, if ever a necromancer were to start raising skeletons we'd have nothing to worry about as they would not be able to get up and start walking.</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl03_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"http://wizards.custhelp.com/cgi-bin/wizards.cfg/php/enduser/ask.php?p_prods=522,706,739&amp;p_cats=\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl03_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '88507'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy21705\">allmighty_abacus</span>\r\n                                (7/16/2010 7:14:59 PM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n<div class=\"starRating\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl03_postRating_starRating\"><img alt=\"0.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"1.0\